title: Xbox 360 The Official Xbox Magazine UK June 2012
description:
Xbox 360 The Official Xbox Magazine UK June 2012

Xbox 360 Official Magazine: The official Xbox magazine, is an exciting multi 
channel gaming experience. For the first time, a magazine, playable demo disc 
and website are all connected and fully interactive, thanks tothe technological
marvel of Xbox Live. For the first time, gamers can easily get involved in their 
community and take control of their Xbox 360 experience.
